name: df-ltpq
body: |- wceq(cltpq, copab(s0, s1, wa(wa(wcel(cv(s0), cxp(cnpi, cnpi)), wcel(cv(s1), cxp(cnpi, cnpi))), wbr(co(cfv(c1st, cv(s0)), cmi, cfv(c2nd, cv(s1))), clti, co(cfv(c1st, cv(s1)), cmi, cfv(c2nd, cv(s0)))))))
comment: Define pre-ordering relation on positive fractions. This is a "temporary" set used in the construction of complex numbers ~ df-c , and is intended to be used only by the construction. Similar to Definition 5 of [Suppes] p. 162. (Contributed by NM, 28-Aug-1995.) (New usage is discouraged.)
